quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  16,43,"Men Nulaani ado maa…óa an Nulaa…óo, si wanaa wor…ìe …ìanndinkoo…ìe, Men wahayina e ma…ì…ìe. Men Nulaali Malaa'ikaa…ìe. ∆äum ko sunna Amen woowaa…óo. Si tawiinon on yeddii …óum, haray lanndee yim…ìe Defte adinoo…óe …óen, …ìen humpitay on wonnde Nulaa…ìe …ìen ko …ìandinnkoo…ìe wonunoo, …ìe wonaano Malaa'ika fes, si tawii on anndaa ko …ìe …ìanndinkoo…ìe."
  16,44,"Men nuliri …ìen Nulaa…ìe …ìanndinkoo…ìe, hujjaaji …ìanngu…ói, e defte jippinaa…óe. Men jippini e maa…óa an Nulaa…óo, Alqur'aana, fii yo a …ìannginan yim…ìe …ìen, ko hatonjini …ìanngineede e mayre, belajo'o kam…ìe …ìe golliray miijooji ma…ì…ìe, …ìe waajitora nde."
  16,45,"E hara …ìen hodu…ìe pewje bon…óe fii falagol e laawol Alla ngol hooli wonnde Alla munnirtaa …ìe leydi ndin wano O munnirnoo ndi Qaaruuna, maa O addirana …ìe lepte …óen nokku mo …ìe habbitoraaki …óe?"
  16,46,"Maa lepte …óen memira …ìe ka yahdu ma…ì…ìe setewu fii faggitagol, …ìe wonaali laawotoo…ìe maa ha…óitotoo…ìe."
  16,47,"Kaa hara …ìe hooli nde lepte Alla …óen nanngirtaa …ìe e hoore kulol majje? Alla ko hattan…óo leptugol …ìe e kala alhaali. Annndu Joomi mon ko Yurmetee…óo Hinnotoo…óo Mo hawjataa yaggingol fii no jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen tuubira …ìe ruttoo ka Makko."
  16,48,"E …ìee fennoo…ìe ndaaraali …ìe taskoo e taguuji Alla …óin, hi…ói yiilora …óow…óe majji √±aamo e nano, jokka yiilagol dillannde e yahdu naange ngen √±alorma, jokka lewru ndun jemma. ∆äin no yannkinanoa Joomi majji sujjangol Mo sujuudu tigiri, hara ko …ói hoynitii…ói."
  16,49,"Ko Alla tun woni ko sujjanta denndaangal ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi, immorde e ruugayngel. Ko Kanko tun Malaa'ikaa…ìe …ìen sujjanta, kam…ìe …ìe townitantaako rewugol Alla …óoftoo Mo."
  16,50,"E hoore ko …ìe duumii e rewugol Mo …óoftoo Mo kon fow, Malaa'ikaa…ìe kan hino hulira Joomi ma…ì…ìe wonir…óo senngo dow ma…ì…ìe Jaati Mun e doole Mun. Hi…ìe golla ko Joomi ma…ì…ìe yamiri …ìe e …óoftagol."
  16,51,"Alla daalani denndaangal jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen: Wata on jogito rewetee…ìe …ói…óo. Anndee rewetee…óo e goonga On ko gooto, O alaa …ói…óa…ìo maa kafidii- …óo. Ko Min woni ko huloton, wanaa go…ó…óum goo."
  16,52,"Ko Kanko Alla tun woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi, tagu e laamu e toppitagol. Ko Kanko tun kadi …óoftaare e yannkinaneede e la…ì…ìinaneede tabitani. E ko ko woori Alla huloton? Aa'a! Ko Kanko tun huloton."
  16,53,"Onon …ìee yim…ìe, kala ko he…ìu…óon e neema diina maa aduna, ko Alla immori, wanaa e go…ó…óo goo. Refti si sa…óteende nawnaare maa baasal memii on, ko Ka Makko tun woni ko wullirton toraare fii yo O huncan on …óum. Awa ye…óoowo neema on, O hunca lorra kan, ko On …óon tun wa…ó…óii reweede."
  16,54,"Refti si toraare mon nde jaabinaama, O huncanii on lorra kan, e jaka fedde goo e mo'on, ko sirkira- noo…ìe Joomi mun kafidugol Mo e goddum goo. Ko hon…óum e aawasaaku nii?"